Django login and room based chat application, similar to Slack

In the chat app we hold everthing about the Django Channels. In the same way we specified a urlpattern, we specified a routing configuration which is specific for wesockets
WS is used to pass info to a specific port.

Install requirements

Open redis docker port with: 
sudo docker run -p 6379:6379 -d redis:5

Make migrations:
python3 manage.py makemigrations
python3 manage.py migrate

Run the server:
python3 manage.py runserver

Opened at http://localhost:8000
